OL,3,CMan who abused easyJet cabin crew and
OL,4,Curinated in front of passengers jailed
OL,6,FA man who abused cabin crew, smoked in
OL,7,Fplane toilets and urinated in front of
OL,8,Fpassengers has been jailed.
OL,10,FBrian Watt was the reason an easyJet
OL,11,Fflight to Tenerife had to be diverted
OL,12,Fto Bristol Airport on 20 April.
OL,14,FHe was intoxicated and caused numerous
OL,15,Fissues on board the plane.
OL,17,FThe 34-year-old smoked in the toilets
OL,18,Fand caused damage to a soap dispenser.
OL,19,FHe refused to remain seated, urinated
OL,20,Fin front of other passengers and was
OL,21,Fabusive to cabin crew.
