OL,3,CMan who abused easyJet cabin crew and
OL,4,Curinated in front of passengers jailed
OL,6,FHe admitted being drunk on an
OL,7,Faircraft, criminal damage, failing to
OL,8,Fobey the lawful commands of the pilot,
OL,9,Fand using threatening, abusive or
OL,10,Finsulting words towards crew.
OL,12,FDuring a hearing at North Somerset
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday 18
OL,14,FJuly, he was sentenced to eight months
OL,15,Fin prison.
