OL,3,CMan who abused easyJet cabin crew and
OL,4,Curinated in front of passengers jailed
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police Sergeant
OL,7,FRachael Hodges said: "Brian Watt's
OL,8,Fthreatening and criminal behaviour was
OL,9,Fdisgraceful, and forced the flight to
OL,10,FTenerife to be diverted. He caused
OL,11,Fsignificant disruption to passengers
OL,12,Fonboard, as well as the airline and
OL,13,Fcrew.
OL,15,F"He now has a criminal record and a
OL,16,Fsignificant prison sentence as a
OL,17,Fresult, and it hopefully is a reminder
OL,18,Fto people flying away this summer of
OL,19,Fthe need to behave when travelling."
